02-08-2017: v1
- Initial release.

10-03-2018: v2
- Add changelog.
- Add WiFi AP search feature on the web interface.

28-03-2019: v3
- Docker based build system.
- Use SendGrid as E-mail notification backend.
- Read ADC during WiFi radio off to get better results.
- State machine around WiFi events and state changes.

21-07-2019: v4
- Using ESP8266 NON-OS SDK 3.0.0.
- Major refactoring and state machine based firmware.
- Improved ADC reading.
- Chip ID based initial device ID.
- Remove battery level measurement code.
